biography: Joakim is a golfer known for his meticulous approach to the game.
While his home club remains a mystery, his dedication to golf is clear. He has participated in the Hector Trophée once, demonstrating his commitment to this prestigious event.

Though success in the form of a Hector Trophée or Victor Trophy has eluded him thus far, Joakim remains an active presence in Hector events, always striving to improve his game. Although he is not currently slated to participate in the upcoming Hector Trophée 2025, golf enthusiasts know that anything can happen, and a last-minute entry is always a possibility. We wish Joakim the best in his future golfing endeavors.
